markdownRemark.html: The golf course is difficult to find without navigation, so be sure to use google below! Close to Malaga Airport (7 km), this an excellently kept course. Lovely old feel and look, especially the club house sitting behind the 18th green. Lots of interesting approaches and on the back 9 water to deal with.
